snippet.title: Official Insurgency Gameplay: Firefight on Market
snippet.description:
This is raw gameplay footage from a single round of Firefight on Market level. A co-ordinated team and individual skill leads to a swift victory.

Firefight can have quick rounds if a team works together like this. All three objectives must be controlled, or eliminate all enemy, to win. Players only respawn when an objective is secured, so matches can last much longer if both teams manage to secure multiple times.

Release date is January 22nd, 2014 so this footage shows the game in Beta.

Buy Insurgency here: http://store.steampowered.com/app/222880/
